            <thetext>Created an attachment (id=1329)
Patch to allow setting unlimited quota through proxy

To (re)set a mailbox quota to unlimited in IMAP, one can use an empty list as parameter of the SETQUOTA command. This however does not work on a proxy server.

The attached patch fixes this issue.</thetext>
